punkte: Vertragsrecht, AGB, Bürgschaft, Handels- und Unternehmensrecht, Bank- und Kapitalmarktrecht, dazu jeweils die internationale Dimension bis hin zum Eurowährungsrecht. Anregend für Juristen dieser Gebiete, mit Ausblicken auf die Konstanten der juristischen Arbeit.  aNorbert Horn combines practical relevance and doctrinal precision with a sense for over-arching economic and legal perspectives and issues of justice. Areas of focus include: contract law, terms and conditions, the laws of guarantees, commerce and corporations, banking and capital markets law, including their international dimensions and Eurocurrency law. This work will stimulate attorneys with an outlook on the constants of legal work.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 23. Jul 2020) 7aLAW / Commercial / General.2bisacsh1 aBerger, Klaus Peter, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHerrmann, Harald, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2016z978311070100508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Law 2016z9783110485202oZDB-23-DGC0 cEPUBz97831104739260 cprintz978311046503740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311047418340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110474183423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110474183.jpg  a978-3-11-070100-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2016b2016  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGCb2016  aZDB-23-DGGb2016